{"sectionId":766,"sectionIdLiteral":"766","humanId":"lesson-342","volumeId":"workbook","locale":"en","titleInfo":{"title":"I let forgiveness rest upon all things,  for thus forgiveness will be given me.","ownlineNumber":"Lesson 342"},"annotation":"W-342","bodyHtml":"<div class=\"acim-text lesson-342\"> <div data-paragraph-id=\"766#1\"><p class=\"p-italic\"><span class=\"pnr\">1.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"766#1:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>I thank You, Father, for Your plan to save me from the hell I made.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"766#1:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>It is not real.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"766#1:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>And You have given me the means to prove its unreality to me.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"766#1:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>The key is in my hand, and I have reached the door beyond which lies the end of dreams.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"766#1:5\"><span class=\"snr\">5</span>I stand before the gate of Heaven, wondering if I should enter in and be at home.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"766#1:6\"><span class=\"snr\">6</span>Let me not wait again today.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"766#1:7\"><span class=\"snr\">7</span>Let me forgive all things, and let creation be as You would have it be and as it is.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"766#1:8\"><span class=\"snr\">8</span>Let me remember that I am Your Son, and opening the door at last, forget illusions in the blazing light of truth, as memory of You returns to me.</span></p></div> <div data-paragraph-id=\"766#2\"><p class=\"p-normal\"><span class=\"pnr\">2.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"766#2:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>Brother, forgive me now.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"766#2:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>I come to you to take you home with me.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"766#2:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>And as we go, the world goes with us on our way to God.</span></p></div> </div>","firstWords":"I thank You, Father, for Your plan to save me from the hell I made. It is not real. And You have given me the means to prove its unreality to me. The key is in my hand, and I have reached the door","contentType":"acim-content","seoTitle":"Lesson 342: I let forgiveness rest upon all‚Ä¶ | ACIM","seoDescription":"‚ú® A Course in Miracles with üéß Audio! Read and listen to Lesson¬†342 ‚ÄúI let forgiveness rest upon all things, for thus forgiveness will be given me‚Äù: I thank You, Father, for Your plan to‚Ä¶","desktopBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"13. What Is a Miracle?","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":764,"slugs":["workbook","what-is-a-miracle"]}},{"label":"Lesson 342","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":766,"slugs":["lesson-342","i-let-forgiveness-rest-upon-all-things-for-thus"]}}],"mobileBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"13. What Is a Miracle?","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":764,"slugs":["workbook","what-is-a-miracle"]}},{"label":"Lesson 342","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":766,"slugs":["lesson-342","i-let-forgiveness-rest-upon-all-things-for-thus"]}}],"seoBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"A Course in Miracles","leadsTo":"dashboard"},{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"13. What Is a Miracle?","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":764,"slugs":["workbook","what-is-a-miracle"]}},{"label":"Lesson 342","leadsTo